  .section
    .row
      h2.text-center.header__bottom-border Frequently Asked Questions
    .row
      .column.large-4.large-offset-2.medium-5.medium-offset-1.small-12
        h5 What exchange rate do my customers get?
        p BitPay always offers the best exchange rate on the market. We pool the order books of all active bitcoin exchanges, and find the best bid worldwide. We call this the Bitcoin Best Bid (BBB) rate, and it is our only rate.
      .column.large-4.medium-5.end
        h5 Do you charge a conversion fee?
        p All of our monthly plans include free and instant conversion to your settlement currency- no percentages. You will be paid the amount you charge.
    .row
      .column.large-4.large-offset-2.medium-5.medium-offset-1.small-12
        h5 Can I get part of my settlement in bitcoin?
        p Many of our merchants choose to take a percentage- or even 100%- of their BitPay settlement in bitcoin. You can choose your settlement preferences from your account dashboard. We settle bitcoin to your bitcoin address daily.
      .column.large-4.medium-5.end
        h5 Can you process payments for regulated businesses?
        p We are able to process for most businesses, but legal and regulatory issues prevent us from servicingsome industries. We'd like to provide all legitimate businesses the opportunity to accept bitcoin, and we are constantly working to make that a possibility.


